<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Fanahy Mpanazava,
 Ny foko hazavao
 Maniry lalandava
 Ny Pentekositrao.
 Ny aizina ao am-poko,
 Fongary re ho lao ;
 Ny foko mitoloko,
 Maniry indrindra Anao !

[V2]
 Fanahy Mpanadio,
 Ny foko mba sasao.
 Diovy re anio
 Ho tena lapanao ;
 Ny hevitray misoko
 Izay te-handroaka Anao,
 Dia ota te-hijoko,
 Esory sy fafao !

[V3]
 Fanahy Mpampahery
 Izay rerakao sy voa,
 Ny foko re dia tery
 Hiantoraka Aminao.
 Izay mandrebireby,
 Roahy re izao,
 Ny fo mitebiteby,
 Hiondana Aminao !
 Amen.</lyrics>
<title>Fanahy Mpanazava FFPM181</title>
<hymn_number>181</hymn_number>
</song>